1
00:01:36,890 --> 00:01:40,150
[Born to Be Alive]

2
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:43,190
[Episode 27]

3
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,500
Even the police can't find him,

4
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,600
what makes you think you can?

5
00:02:14,410 --> 00:02:15,090
What?

6
00:02:15,730 --> 00:02:17,190
Do I have to open it for you?

7
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,160
Back in the Mountain Patrol,

8
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:39,030
you guys always kept an eye on me

9
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:41,770
and wouldn't let me drink.

10
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,750
Drink up.

11
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:47,690
Now no one's there to nag you anymore.

12
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,600
That's right.

13
00:02:56,930 --> 00:02:58,930
Now no one's there to nag me anymore.

14
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,370
No one...

15
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,620
You haven't even started drinking.

16
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:43,680
Why are you crying?

17
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:47,700
No one's there to nag me anymore.

18
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:03,430
Mr. Feng.

19
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:05,130
Meng,

20
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:06,880
you're just in time.

21
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:09,120
Liao from Chenlong Coal Mine

22
00:04:09,740 --> 00:04:11,070
sent over a set of clubs.

23
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,460
Take them and have fun.

24
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:13,690
Thank you.

25
00:04:14,190 --> 00:04:15,600
But golf...

26
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:17,089
I don't know how to play it.

27
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:19,050
It's mostly about taking a walk.

28
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:19,920
Don't just

29
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,360
sit in the office all the time.

30
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,960
Get out and move around more.

31
00:04:23,690 --> 00:04:24,300
Here.

32
00:04:24,930 --> 00:04:25,730
Have some tea.

33
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:29,640
Liao is still so stingy.

34
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:30,830
He didn't even

35
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:32,300
pick a good brand.

36
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,540
I think

37
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:36,750
we should knock
another twenty million off

38
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:38,680
the final price for Chenlong Mine.

39
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:42,530
For a small matter like this,

40
00:04:42,930 --> 00:04:45,390
you two can just decide
between yourselves.

41
00:04:47,659 --> 00:04:48,300
Mr. Feng,

42
00:04:48,770 --> 00:04:50,010
I've contacted

43
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,270
those mine owners.

44
00:04:51,930 --> 00:04:53,810
They are the ones in a rush now.

45
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,680
They've shut down production

46
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,659
but still have to keep paying the workers.

47
00:04:57,659 --> 00:04:58,690
They're all begging

48
00:04:58,690 --> 00:05:00,620
to sign the contract with us
as soon as possible.

49
00:05:00,620 --> 00:05:01,420
Really?

50
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:03,810
I heard Dajin Coal Mine

51
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:04,920
is still sticking to 500 million

52
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,850
and won't budge.

53
00:05:07,690 --> 00:05:10,090
Some of them are
trying to jack up the price.

54
00:05:10,210 --> 00:05:11,560
But I've looked into it.

55
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:13,300
They don't have any backing.

56
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,860
If they dare to act tough with me again,

57
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:16,770
I have plenty of ways

58
00:05:16,770 --> 00:05:18,160
to shut them up.

59
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:21,270
What kind of ways?

60
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:22,940
Blocking the gate?

61
00:05:22,940 --> 00:05:24,370
Cutting off water and power?

62
00:05:24,370 --> 00:05:25,830
Or just beating people up?

63
00:05:26,770 --> 00:05:27,560
Wu.

64
00:05:28,250 --> 00:05:29,980
It's not ten years ago anymore.

65
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,450
Vice Mayor Lin's secretary

66
00:05:31,450 --> 00:05:32,450
called me just now

67
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,690
and specifically emphasized the need

68
00:05:33,690 --> 00:05:36,550
for the consolidation
to comply with regulations.

69
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:38,720
Don't get it?

70
00:05:40,330 --> 00:05:41,750
He's warning us

71
00:05:41,770 --> 00:05:42,600
that at a time like this,

72
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,980
do not cause trouble.

73
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,190
Vice Mayor Lin?

74
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:49,210
With Mr. Feng's

75
00:05:49,210 --> 00:05:50,940
relationship with Mayor Wang,

76
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:51,840
why are you

77
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:52,330
afraid of him, a Vice Mayor?

78
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:53,790
If you two keep bickering,

79
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,750
I'm going back to my island.

80
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,080
I just told you.

81
00:05:59,460 --> 00:06:00,560
For a small matter like this,

82
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,510
you two can just decide
between yourselves.

83
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:04,370
Don't bother me with everything.

84
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:05,630
Yes, sir.

85
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,530
Understood.

86
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,330
I read your report.

87
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,290
It was very good.

88
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,830
Just now, I even praised you

89
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,100
in front of Mayor Wang.

90
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,030
What are your thoughts

91
00:06:15,220 --> 00:06:16,760
after this inspection trip?

92
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:17,920
If there is anything else

93
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,870
you need the city government

94
00:06:18,870 --> 00:06:19,890
to help with,

95
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:20,930
just ask.

96
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:24,240
Then, I won't beat around the bush

97
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,040
with you.

98
00:06:26,060 --> 00:06:26,650
When have you ever

99
00:06:26,650 --> 00:06:28,380
beaten around the bush with me?

100
00:06:28,570 --> 00:06:29,390
Just say it.

101
00:06:30,740 --> 00:06:31,930
My previous report

102
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,470
was initially coordinated

103
00:06:33,470 --> 00:06:34,890
by the Tianduo Coal Bureau.

104
00:06:34,890 --> 00:06:35,480
They wanted

105
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,360
to use an undercover media investigation

106
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,480
to break the deadlock,

107
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,659
then team up with workplace safety,

108
00:06:38,659 --> 00:06:39,310
environmental,

109
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,130
industry and commerce,

110
00:06:40,130 --> 00:06:41,150
and land resources authorities

111
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:42,360
to carry out a major crackdown

112
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,020
on Tianduo's coal companies.

113
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:45,560
But later on,

114
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:46,850
they restricted my coverage

115
00:06:46,850 --> 00:06:49,980
to only the problems
involving small and mid-sized mines.

116
00:06:49,980 --> 00:06:51,840
Substandard production safety,

117
00:06:51,930 --> 00:06:53,159
mining beyond boundaries,

118
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,500
inadequate dust control,

119
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:55,320
and grassland pollution—

120
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,180
These problems

121
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:56,800
also exist

122
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:58,280
in Xinhai's mining areas.

123
00:07:00,450 --> 00:07:01,250
I understand.

124
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,190
What you said

125
00:07:05,330 --> 00:07:06,570
is indeed the truth.

126
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:08,830
But after all,

127
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:11,030
Xinhai operates on such a massive scale

128
00:07:11,170 --> 00:07:12,300
and has so many pits.

129
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,370
If these issues

130
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,500
were concentrated in one mine,

131
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:18,020
that would indeed be a problem.

132
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:18,620
But

133
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,580
when they're scattered across

134
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:21,500
Xinhai's pits,

135
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:23,620
the problem actually

136
00:07:23,620 --> 00:07:24,790
isn't that serious.

137
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:26,630
Furthermore,

138
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,010
coal

139
00:07:28,450 --> 00:07:30,180
is Tianduo's pillar industry.

140
00:07:30,540 --> 00:07:31,870
As the leader in charge,

141
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:34,430
he must consider tax revenue.

142
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:35,620
So, Huang

143
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:38,360
gave your editor-in-chief a heads-up.

144
00:07:38,570 --> 00:07:39,210
You need

145
00:07:40,110 --> 00:07:42,170
to be more understanding about this.

146
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:47,600
I'm not some rookie

147
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:48,800
who just started working.

148
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,880
Raising the hammer high,

149
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:50,940
only to tap gently.

150
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:53,030
I've seen this plenty of times.

151
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,100
You still

152
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,490
talk so harshly.

153
00:07:59,690 --> 00:08:00,500
At first, I also thought

154
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:01,870
it was just like before,

155
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:04,120
that the leaders were afraid
that if the issues were spread out,

156
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,680
it would cause more serious troubles.

157
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,810
Until a few days ago,

158
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,700
when it was proposed at the meeting

159
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:08,770
that Xinhai should take the lead

160
00:08:08,770 --> 00:08:10,520
in consolidating those coal mines,

161
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,450
I couldn't help but be suspicious.

162
00:08:19,310 --> 00:08:20,300
Do you think

163
00:08:21,020 --> 00:08:22,770
there's a problem with the consolidation?

164
00:08:22,770 --> 00:08:23,190
No,

165
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:24,620
there's nothing wrong

166
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:26,420
with the consolidation itself.

167
00:08:26,420 --> 00:08:27,030
But when you

168
00:08:27,030 --> 00:08:28,630
piece everything together,

169
00:08:28,740 --> 00:08:30,470
that's where the problem lies.

170
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:33,580
First, a reporter is brought in
for an undercover probe

171
00:08:33,580 --> 00:08:34,549
to expose violations

172
00:08:34,549 --> 00:08:35,610
at the small mines.

173
00:08:36,010 --> 00:08:37,049
Then the authorities

174
00:08:37,049 --> 00:08:38,169
act swiftly,

175
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:40,360
ordering an immediate shutdown
for rectification.

176
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,460
And right then,

177
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:42,600
the "perfect" Xinhai Group,

178
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:44,390
the only company with a clean record,

179
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:46,250
steps in like a savior.

180
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,580
They propose

181
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,770
a takeover plan

182
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:51,810
and use it as a stepping stone
to expand their empire.

183
00:08:53,050 --> 00:08:53,920
Don't you think

184
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,870
it's all just a bit too convenient?

185
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:58,960
I've basically been used

186
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,420
as a weapon in their hands.

187
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:19,720
Shao,

188
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:24,300
you've made

189
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:26,600
a very serious accusation.

190
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,480
It's just my theory.

191
00:09:33,210 --> 00:09:33,800
I also hope

192
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,260
I'm just overthinking it.

193
00:09:38,370 --> 00:09:40,080
So, in your theory,

194
00:09:41,050 --> 00:09:43,310
what role do I,
the Executive Vice Mayor,

195
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:45,960
am playing in all this?

196
00:09:53,940 --> 00:09:54,830
Who proposed

197
00:09:54,850 --> 00:09:56,580
this consolidation plan?

198
00:09:58,170 --> 00:09:59,080
Was it proposed

199
00:09:59,100 --> 00:10:00,490
before or after

200
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,580
my report came out?

201
00:10:03,660 --> 00:10:05,060
You might not believe it.

202
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:07,600
I haven't known

203
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,750
about this plan

204
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:11,300
much longer than you have.

205
00:10:11,890 --> 00:10:13,290
Of course, I believe you.

206
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:16,510
To be honest,

207
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,170
I share

208
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:20,820
your concerns.

209
00:10:23,010 --> 00:10:24,460
But procedurally speaking,

210
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:25,720
everything

211
00:10:26,250 --> 00:10:27,650
is legal and legitimate.

212
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:29,100
I...

213
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:31,660
I have no grounds

214
00:10:32,070 --> 00:10:33,060
to object.

215
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,600
I still want

216
00:10:39,170 --> 00:10:40,830
to investigate Xinhai Group.

217
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:42,900
I hope you can support me.

218
00:10:48,290 --> 00:10:49,580
Here. It's from a new milk tea shop.

219
00:10:49,580 --> 00:10:51,700
I waited in line
for twenty minutes for it.

220
00:10:51,700 --> 00:10:53,030
No thanks, you drink it.

221
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:55,460
It's low sugar. Taste it.

222
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:56,390
Don't you know the taste

223
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:56,860
of the milk tea

224
00:10:56,860 --> 00:10:57,860
we usually drink?

225
00:11:00,990 --> 00:11:01,600
I...

226
00:11:11,110 --> 00:11:12,360
I heard you threw out your back.

227
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,090
Are you okay?

228
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:14,190
What did you want to see me about?

229
00:11:14,190 --> 00:11:15,330
Just say it.

230
00:11:18,180 --> 00:11:19,910
I wanted to talk about it at home

231
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:21,630
and ask Mom for her opinion.

232
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,080
I...

233
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:27,150
Ask Lingling's grandmother

234
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:28,200
for her opinion.

235
00:11:29,970 --> 00:11:31,750
I still want to take you and Lingling

236
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,680
to live in the provincial capital.

237
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:34,620
You've told me about this

238
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:36,260
many times already.

239
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,300
I told you, I don't agree.

240
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,720
Besides, we're already—

241
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,930
Divorced. I know.

242
00:11:45,050 --> 00:11:45,670
I'm doing this

243
00:11:45,670 --> 00:11:47,270
for the child's sake.

244
00:11:47,370 --> 00:11:48,000
After all,

245
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:48,980
the educational resources
in the provincial capital

246
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:50,030
are better than here.

247
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:51,630
Only a tiny fraction of students here
get into top-tier schools.

248
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:52,210
She will have to

249
00:11:52,210 --> 00:11:53,870
leave this place eventually.

250
00:11:55,030 --> 00:11:55,770
As for

251
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:58,060
other matters,

252
00:11:58,510 --> 00:12:00,040
I haven't thought that far.

253
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:03,500
Shao Yunfei.

254
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,020
Not everyone

255
00:12:06,250 --> 00:12:07,390
wants to leave.

256
00:12:09,050 --> 00:12:10,120
From when we were good

257
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,180
to when we split up,

258
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:13,600
I've always

259
00:12:13,620 --> 00:12:15,020
respected your choices.

260
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:16,770
I also hope

261
00:12:16,770 --> 00:12:17,340
you won't use

262
00:12:17,340 --> 00:12:18,120
Lingling as an excuse

263
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,580
to interfere with my life.

264
00:12:20,630 --> 00:12:22,160
The child needs her mother.

265
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,980
But she also needs her father.

266
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:25,190
But you didn't

267
00:12:25,190 --> 00:12:26,990
stay in Tianduo because of that.

268
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,320
Back then, you told me

269
00:12:28,370 --> 00:12:29,700
to go back
and work in the provincial capital.

270
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:30,350
I told you to go,

271
00:12:30,350 --> 00:12:30,980
and you just did?

272
00:12:30,980 --> 00:12:31,380
You...

273
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,390
Forget it.

274
00:12:37,980 --> 00:12:39,720
There's no point in bringing up the past.

275
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,520
That's right.

276
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:42,440
You think provincial capital schools

277
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,090
are better—

278
00:12:43,090 --> 00:12:44,180
That was then.

279
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:46,900
These days, Tianduo's resources

280
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:47,940
and facilities

281
00:12:48,050 --> 00:12:49,460
are just as good.

282
00:12:49,890 --> 00:12:50,500
We have several

283
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:52,000
"Aid-to-Qinghai" schools

284
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,200
where teachers from Beijing

285
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,000
are actually leading the classes.

286
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,650
Besides,

287
00:12:55,950 --> 00:12:57,980
the competition in the provincial capital
is fierce,

288
00:12:57,980 --> 00:12:58,920
and the pressure is huge.

289
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,320
Lingling is still young.

290
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:01,240
I just want her

291
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,530
to be free and happy.

292
00:13:03,290 --> 00:13:03,930
Plus, she has

293
00:13:03,930 --> 00:13:05,190
friends here.

294
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:05,940
If she goes there,

295
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:07,550
she'll have to readapt to everything.

296
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:08,710
Kids are very

297
00:13:08,740 --> 00:13:09,620
adaptable.

298
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:14,920
Also, transferring my job

299
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:15,980
isn't that simple.

300
00:13:18,050 --> 00:13:18,620
Going there

301
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:20,790
to sit in a government office job
would be boring.

302
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:21,220
I'm not the type

303
00:13:21,220 --> 00:13:22,240
who can sit still.

304
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:27,410
You really haven't changed a bit.

305
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:31,080
What do you mean by that?

306
00:13:34,980 --> 00:13:35,360
I know

307
00:13:35,390 --> 00:13:36,620
why you don't want to leave.

308
00:13:36,620 --> 00:13:37,410
My lunch break

309
00:13:37,410 --> 00:13:38,270
is almost over.

310
00:13:38,270 --> 00:13:39,730
Get your things and leave.

311
00:13:50,060 --> 00:13:52,630
[Xinhai Coal Mine]

312
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:02,510
Come in.

313
00:14:07,470 --> 00:14:08,880
What is this?

314
00:14:09,050 --> 00:14:10,240
Mr. Feng gave it to me.

315
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:12,170
He told me to learn how to play golf.

316
00:14:13,330 --> 00:14:15,120
If he has time to play,

317
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:17,270
shouldn't he think about the mine?

318
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:19,030
If you have time
to complain about him,

319
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:19,750
why don't you think about

320
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:21,170
your own personal life?

321
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:24,010
Well.

322
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:24,840
The consolidation plan

323
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,120
for small and medium coal mines in Tianduo

324
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,720
has been officially approved.

325
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:29,180
Xinhai is taking the lead.

326
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,820
I want

327
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,800
to bring you on board.

328
00:14:32,890 --> 00:14:34,890
I'm fine with managing production.

329
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:38,000
But when it comes
to business consolidation,

330
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,770
I'm really a layman.

331
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,680
You're in your 40s this year.

332
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,940
Do you really plan
to stay on the front line

333
00:14:48,940 --> 00:14:50,250
for the rest of your life?

334
00:14:50,250 --> 00:14:51,220
If you don't take over now,

335
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:51,770
in another 10 years,

336
00:14:51,770 --> 00:14:53,170
you'll still be a layman.

337
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:54,050
And then what?

338
00:14:54,190 --> 00:14:56,190
Just waiting to be “optimized out?”

339
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:04,650
You said before

340
00:15:04,710 --> 00:15:05,980
the group would make a big move.

341
00:15:05,980 --> 00:15:06,780
Is this it?

342
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:08,030
Take a good look.

343
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:10,640
This is the toughest nut to crack.

344
00:15:11,310 --> 00:15:12,420
The ownership of this pasture

345
00:15:12,420 --> 00:15:13,880
is problematic, isn't it?

346
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:14,720
Yes.

347
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:18,040
It's a problem left over from the past.

348
00:15:18,980 --> 00:15:19,770
In this rectification,

349
00:15:19,770 --> 00:15:20,500
we've acquired

350
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:21,290
a massive stretch of land

351
00:15:21,290 --> 00:15:22,890
from the Chenlong Coal Mine.

352
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:25,000
But as of now, there are still people

353
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,930
leasing that pasture for grazing.

354
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:31,630
This pasture

355
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:33,650
is very close to the Chenlong mining area.

356
00:15:33,650 --> 00:15:35,550
It's no longer suitable for grazing.

357
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:36,120
Exactly.

358
00:15:36,550 --> 00:15:37,270
That's why the company

359
00:15:37,270 --> 00:15:38,150
wants to take it over

360
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:40,350
to use as a dumping ground for coal slag.

361
00:15:40,510 --> 00:15:41,790
The catch is

362
00:15:41,890 --> 00:15:42,980
that the original contract

363
00:15:42,980 --> 00:15:43,960
between the owner and Chenlong

364
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:44,720
has already

365
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:45,740
expired.

366
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:48,270
So you're worried the owner

367
00:15:48,370 --> 00:15:49,850
won't agree to let Xinhai
develop the land?

368
00:15:49,850 --> 00:15:50,300
Right.

369
00:15:51,650 --> 00:15:53,120
The biggest problem

370
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:54,920
is the owner of this pasture.

371
00:15:55,650 --> 00:15:56,720
Cairen.

372
00:15:58,890 --> 00:16:00,890
This is County Mayor Duo's pasture?

373
00:16:31,890 --> 00:16:32,670
Dad.

374
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:34,870
I've come to see you.

375
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:36,580
Tashi Delek.

376
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:37,960
Tashi Delek.

377
00:16:38,710 --> 00:16:40,570
Did you quarrel with Bai Ju again?

378
00:16:43,670 --> 00:16:45,220
You big jinx!

379
00:16:47,690 --> 00:16:49,220
What was it about this time?

380
00:16:51,700 --> 00:16:52,120
Here.

381
00:16:53,650 --> 00:16:55,630
Did you go skinning animals again?

382
00:16:56,930 --> 00:16:58,360
You'd rather starve to death

383
00:16:58,360 --> 00:17:00,140
than do that kind of thing.

384
00:17:00,580 --> 00:17:01,770
Let aside Ju,

385
00:17:02,050 --> 00:17:03,250
even the sacred mountains

386
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:04,660
and the earth will frown upon you!

387
00:17:04,660 --> 00:17:05,349
Okay, okay.

388
00:17:05,460 --> 00:17:06,440
I won't do it anymore.

389
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,560
Don't be angry.

390
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:08,849
Okay, okay.

391
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:16,200
Do I...

392
00:17:16,430 --> 00:17:18,089
Do I look that much like Bai Ji?

393
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:28,280
Bai Ju doesn't want to leave.

394
00:17:29,050 --> 00:17:30,110
She likes it here.

395
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:31,690
Don't use the child

396
00:17:31,690 --> 00:17:32,630
to force her.

397
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:34,980
If she just liked it here,

398
00:17:34,980 --> 00:17:36,040
that would be fine.

399
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:37,470
You know

400
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:38,630
why she won't leave.

401
00:17:39,050 --> 00:17:40,760
Her heart is still trapped there.

402
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:42,020
And you can't help her.

403
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:43,460
That's right.

404
00:17:44,630 --> 00:17:45,870
I can't help anyone.

405
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:48,180
I went back,

406
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:48,610
but I didn't

407
00:17:48,610 --> 00:17:50,000
become a good reporter.

408
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:53,640
After all these years,

409
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:55,090
nothing has changed.

410
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:58,370
Things have changed, you know.

411
00:17:58,370 --> 00:17:59,170
Look at me.

412
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,720
I've traded the family pasture

413
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,250
for shares in the coal mine.

414
00:18:02,850 --> 00:18:03,390
My wife and child

415
00:18:03,390 --> 00:18:04,850
are living in the city now.

416
00:18:05,590 --> 00:18:06,200
The kid can go to

417
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,370
a better school.

418
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:10,960
And I have it now.

419
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:13,410
I'll take you for a ride later.

420
00:18:18,350 --> 00:18:19,610
Looking at it this way,

421
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:22,170
development is still good.

422
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,730
Three steps forward, two steps back.

423
00:18:25,730 --> 00:18:27,860
It's still one step forward in the end.

424
00:18:28,600 --> 00:18:29,660
More than one step.

425
00:18:30,590 --> 00:18:31,640
Hit the gas

426
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:32,790
and it's tens of thousands.

427
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:33,190
Can...

428
00:18:33,350 --> 00:18:34,090
can you stop

429
00:18:34,590 --> 00:18:35,550
talking about your car?

430
00:18:35,550 --> 00:18:36,950
I feel like we're just not

431
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:38,830
on the same wavelength anymore.

432
00:18:38,830 --> 00:18:39,640
I get it.

433
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:40,710
You're

434
00:18:41,110 --> 00:18:42,510
having a midlife crisis.

435
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:45,830
Where are you getting all this from?

436
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:46,880
But...

437
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:50,010
Xinhai has started

438
00:18:50,010 --> 00:18:52,410
consolidating small coal mines recently.

439
00:18:52,810 --> 00:18:53,270
The land

440
00:18:54,020 --> 00:18:55,550
around here might all get rezoned

441
00:18:55,550 --> 00:18:57,030
in the next phase.

442
00:19:00,350 --> 00:19:02,080
Does that affect this pasture?

443
00:19:03,010 --> 00:19:03,820
Maybe.

444
00:19:05,620 --> 00:19:07,190
You'd better be prepared.

445
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:22,170
Although I gave my family pasture

446
00:19:22,660 --> 00:19:23,640
to the coal mine,

447
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:27,680
I want

448
00:19:29,660 --> 00:19:30,760
to guard this pasture

449
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:31,820
for as long as I can.

450
00:19:38,270 --> 00:19:39,200
Do you regret it?

451
00:19:42,090 --> 00:19:43,670
Yaks follow the herdsman.

452
00:19:44,970 --> 00:19:46,630
The herdsman follows the sun.

453
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:50,550
Patrolling with Captain Duojie

454
00:19:52,090 --> 00:19:52,960
was the most worthwhile thing

455
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:54,250
in my life.

456
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:55,520
Well said!

457
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:02,700
Advice.

458
00:20:03,890 --> 00:20:04,760
Advice.

459
00:20:08,290 --> 00:20:08,920
More.

460
00:20:09,450 --> 00:20:10,080
More.

461
00:20:10,770 --> 00:20:11,350
Why are you looking at me?

462
00:20:11,350 --> 00:20:12,460
Look at your notebook.

463
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:13,520
Write it yourself.

464
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,400
Write.

465
00:20:20,340 --> 00:20:20,870
Alright.

466
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:21,560
Let me see.

467
00:20:27,090 --> 00:20:27,830
You'll need to work faster

468
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:29,250
on your homework from now on.

469
00:20:29,250 --> 00:20:30,000
You need to focus.

470
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:30,730
Understand?

471
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:32,470
Okay.

472
00:20:33,180 --> 00:20:33,620
What other homework

473
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:35,280
do you have left for this week?

474
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:38,240
Only the weekly diary is left.

475
00:20:38,330 --> 00:20:39,180
Let me check it

476
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,330
after you finish it.

477
00:20:40,370 --> 00:20:41,330
Mom,

478
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,810
that's my privacy.

479
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:43,880
What privacy?

480
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:45,060
Last time,

481
00:20:45,060 --> 00:20:46,010
you copied directly from the essay book.

482
00:20:46,010 --> 00:20:47,130
Your teacher told me about it.

483
00:20:47,130 --> 00:20:48,460
You think I didn't know?

484
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:49,730
Hurry up and write.

485
00:20:49,730 --> 00:20:51,460
I'll check it when you're done.

486
00:20:51,670 --> 00:20:52,330
Chop-chop.

487
00:20:53,010 --> 00:20:54,270
You need to have a proper attitude
towards studying,

488
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:54,970
you know?

489
00:20:55,850 --> 00:20:56,500
Lingling,

490
00:20:57,520 --> 00:20:58,450
have some fruit.

491
00:20:58,450 --> 00:20:59,560
Thanks, Grandma.

492
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:00,500
Rest for a while.

493
00:21:00,500 --> 00:21:01,530
Mom, she just started writing,

494
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:03,370
and you're letting her rest again.

495
00:21:03,370 --> 00:21:05,170
Come inside with me for a second.

496
00:21:07,570 --> 00:21:09,010
Finish eating and get to your homework.

497
00:21:09,010 --> 00:21:10,000
Stop fidgeting and focus.

498
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:10,430
Get it?

499
00:21:14,220 --> 00:21:14,900
Mom,

500
00:21:15,070 --> 00:21:16,910
I was educating the child.

501
00:21:17,070 --> 00:21:18,500
Why did you interrupt?

502
00:21:19,830 --> 00:21:20,840
I also want to educate

503
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:21,640
my child.

504
00:21:22,830 --> 00:21:23,810
What did I do?

505
00:21:24,770 --> 00:21:25,270
Shao

506
00:21:25,300 --> 00:21:27,230
went to your workplace to find you?

507
00:21:29,850 --> 00:21:31,180
What did you talk about?

508
00:21:31,470 --> 00:21:32,310
Nothing much.

509
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,160
I don't care

510
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,240
what he tells you—

511
00:21:35,630 --> 00:21:37,360
don't you try to talk me into it.

512
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:39,000
I'm not Ji.

513
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:40,620
I won't side with outsiders.

514
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:43,620
I just hope

515
00:21:44,300 --> 00:21:45,020
that there's someone

516
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:46,450
to keep you company.

517
00:21:47,290 --> 00:21:48,750
It doesn't have to be Shao.

518
00:21:59,110 --> 00:21:59,890
What?

519
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:01,760
Take a look.

520
00:22:10,540 --> 00:22:11,500
What's this for?

521
00:22:11,520 --> 00:22:12,980
What's this for?

522
00:22:14,810 --> 00:22:15,860
He's Ms. Wang's son.

523
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:17,060
Who is Ms. Wang?

524
00:22:17,140 --> 00:22:19,200
She came to our hospital as a patient.

525
00:22:19,420 --> 00:22:20,530
She's very warm.

526
00:22:21,470 --> 00:22:22,320
Her son,

527
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:22,940
right now—

528
00:22:22,940 --> 00:22:23,570
Mom,

529
00:22:23,910 --> 00:22:25,050
I'm forty.

530
00:22:25,090 --> 00:22:26,600
Her son is a few years older than you.

531
00:22:26,600 --> 00:22:27,800
The age is perfect.

532
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,310
He's a company executive

533
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:29,920
and successful in his career.

534
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:31,980
My daughter is already ten years old.

535
00:22:31,990 --> 00:22:33,700
He has never been married,

536
00:22:33,870 --> 00:22:34,800
has no children,

537
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:36,020
and he doesn't mind it.

538
00:22:36,020 --> 00:22:36,670
I mean,

539
00:22:36,770 --> 00:22:38,140
at my age,

540
00:22:39,660 --> 00:22:40,790
I'm... at that point

541
00:22:40,970 --> 00:22:41,740
where in a couple of years,

542
00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:42,280
just a single sneeze

543
00:22:42,280 --> 00:22:43,610
could throw my back out.

544
00:22:43,860 --> 00:22:45,050
Why... Why are you arranging this

545
00:22:45,050 --> 00:22:45,850
for me?

546
00:22:46,530 --> 00:22:47,140
Your back

547
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,380
might be fine

548
00:22:48,410 --> 00:22:49,360
by then.

549
00:22:50,580 --> 00:22:52,640
Just think of it as making a new friend.

550
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:53,500
And he might not

551
00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:54,450
be interested in you.

552
00:22:54,450 --> 00:22:55,500
What are you afraid of?

553
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:55,830
I—

554
00:22:56,930 --> 00:22:57,870
Just go meet him.

555
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:01,640
If you have time to worry about me,

556
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:02,370
why don't you think

557
00:23:02,370 --> 00:23:04,250
about Bai Chun's personal situation?

558
00:23:04,250 --> 00:23:05,110
I'm not the only one

559
00:23:05,110 --> 00:23:06,450
single in this family.

560
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,020
Captain.

561
00:23:15,890 --> 00:23:16,290
Okay.

562
00:23:16,310 --> 00:23:16,870
I get it.

563
00:23:17,270 --> 00:23:18,400
I'm going right now.

564
00:23:19,050 --> 00:23:20,050
Don't mention it.

565
00:23:20,370 --> 00:23:20,780
Okay.

566
00:23:21,270 --> 00:23:22,470
Do you have a mission?

567
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,030
Captain's parent

568
00:23:24,030 --> 00:23:25,030
is having emergency surgery,

569
00:23:25,030 --> 00:23:26,560
so he has to go check on them.

570
00:23:26,610 --> 00:23:27,040
Remember

571
00:23:27,040 --> 00:23:28,970
to check Lingling's weekly dairy.

572
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:30,270
Last time she wrote

573
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:31,320
that she wants

574
00:23:31,320 --> 00:23:33,110
to be a firefighter like her dad.

575
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:33,760
The teacher

576
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:35,160
thought I got remarried.

577
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:35,950
I know.

578
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,890
What's wrong with remarrying?

579
00:24:17,370 --> 00:24:17,780
Hello.

580
00:24:17,870 --> 00:24:18,310
Police.

581
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:19,300
Routine inspection.

582
00:24:19,300 --> 00:24:20,050
Please cooperate.

583
00:24:20,050 --> 00:24:20,380
Okay.

584
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:20,830
Okay.

585
00:24:21,130 --> 00:24:21,870
Where is V01?

586
00:24:21,900 --> 00:24:22,490
Take us there.

587
00:24:22,490 --> 00:24:22,820
Okay.

588
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:29,620
♪ The song is like the bright spring... ♪

589
00:24:28,090 --> 00:24:28,820
Stop singing

590
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:31,290
Police.

591
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:33,940
Put down everything in your hands.

592
00:24:33,940 --> 00:24:34,470
Put down.

593
00:24:37,840 --> 00:24:38,270
Well...

594
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:38,800
Sit down.

595
00:24:45,960 --> 00:24:47,220
Give the camera to Wang.

596
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:48,490
You organize the urine tests.

597
00:24:48,490 --> 00:24:49,880
Where are you going, Captain?

598
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:50,400
I'll step out

599
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:51,720
and call my superiors to report.

600
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:53,320
My immediate family is here.

601
00:24:54,080 --> 00:24:54,610
Go ahead.

602
00:24:58,020 --> 00:24:59,000
Get your IDs out

603
00:24:59,020 --> 00:25:00,080
for registration.

604
00:25:03,250 --> 00:25:04,230
I am Bai Ju's brother,

605
00:25:04,230 --> 00:25:04,760
Bai Chun.

606
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:10,290
Who is

607
00:25:11,170 --> 00:25:11,950
Meng Yaohui?

608
00:25:13,070 --> 00:25:14,330
Okay, I understand.

609
00:25:15,300 --> 00:25:16,230
I'll be careful.

610
00:25:16,290 --> 00:25:16,800
Careful.

611
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:17,860
Careful. Careful.

612
00:25:18,150 --> 00:25:18,650
Okay.

613
00:25:21,080 --> 00:25:22,410
Which room are you from?

614
00:25:23,940 --> 00:25:24,920
V01.

615
00:25:25,110 --> 00:25:25,910
What's wrong?

616
00:25:37,040 --> 00:25:38,060
What's your name?

617
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:39,800
Meng Yaohui.

618
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:42,110
She is my client.

619
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:43,830
I just came out of the restroom

620
00:25:43,830 --> 00:25:44,800
and saw she was drunk,

621
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:45,540
so I helped her.

622
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:46,780
We received a report

623
00:25:46,900 --> 00:25:48,030
that you were leading people here

624
00:25:48,030 --> 00:25:49,920
to use illegal substances

625
00:25:50,990 --> 00:25:52,510
and engage in illegal activities.

626
00:25:52,510 --> 00:25:55,040
Go inside and cooperate
with the inspection.

627
00:25:55,290 --> 00:25:56,220
Take him inside.

628
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:56,820
Let's go.

629
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:03,370
Wu Jinxuan.

630
00:26:03,470 --> 00:26:04,180
Check it.

631
00:26:04,220 --> 00:26:05,830
The urine test result is negative.

632
00:26:05,830 --> 00:26:06,990
If there's no problem, sign here.

633
00:26:06,990 --> 00:26:08,120
There's no problem.

634
00:26:11,940 --> 00:26:12,620
Take it.

635
00:26:13,770 --> 00:26:14,300
Captain.

636
00:26:14,330 --> 00:26:15,190
We've checked.

637
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:16,590
Everyone's urine test results

638
00:26:16,590 --> 00:26:17,390
are negative.

639
00:26:17,420 --> 00:26:18,080
No issues.

640
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:20,030
Have all their identities been confirmed?

641
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:20,690
Yes.

642
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:21,720
They are all

643
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:23,250
employees of Xinhai Coal Mine

644
00:26:23,250 --> 00:26:24,310
and their clients.

645
00:26:25,510 --> 00:26:25,990
Okay.

646
00:26:27,870 --> 00:26:28,390
The suspicion

647
00:26:28,390 --> 00:26:29,960
of drug use and other illegal conduct

648
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:30,960
has been ruled out

649
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:31,610
for now.

650
00:26:32,800 --> 00:26:34,600
Thank you for your cooperation.

651
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:36,170
Let's go.

652
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:37,580
Mr. Wang, wait a moment.

653
00:26:37,580 --> 00:26:38,350
Officer.

654
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,000
I'd like to ask,

655
00:26:43,740 --> 00:26:45,080
who reported us?

656
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:47,260
We have regulations.

657
00:26:47,260 --> 00:26:47,880
We cannot reveal

658
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:49,410
the informant's identity.

659
00:26:49,850 --> 00:26:51,030
I suspect

660
00:26:51,290 --> 00:26:53,010
someone filed a malicious report.

661
00:26:53,010 --> 00:26:53,930
Don't you deal with

662
00:26:53,930 --> 00:26:55,110
the false report?

663
00:26:55,760 --> 00:26:56,430
When we get back,

664
00:26:56,430 --> 00:26:57,850
we will investigate it.

665
00:26:58,590 --> 00:27:00,400
If there's a false report,

666
00:27:00,970 --> 00:27:03,100
we will handle it according to the law.

667
00:27:04,170 --> 00:27:05,370
Any other questions?

668
00:27:09,110 --> 00:27:09,610
No.

669
00:27:10,250 --> 00:27:10,850
Thank you.

670
00:27:12,980 --> 00:27:13,510
Let's go.

671
00:27:32,490 --> 00:27:33,440
I've passed this shop

672
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:34,650
many times,

673
00:27:35,370 --> 00:27:36,790
but this is my first time coming in.

674
00:27:36,790 --> 00:27:37,630
I heard from my mom

675
00:27:37,630 --> 00:27:38,760
that you are a local.

676
00:27:40,590 --> 00:27:41,090
Yes.

677
00:27:42,970 --> 00:27:44,100
But...

678
00:27:44,710 --> 00:27:46,380
I've been busy with work,

679
00:27:46,910 --> 00:27:48,840
so I'm not familiar with this area.

680
00:27:50,280 --> 00:27:51,940
Do you go on blind dates often?

681
00:27:54,490 --> 00:27:56,020
Why do you need blind dates?

682
00:27:56,330 --> 00:27:57,110
With your condition,

683
00:27:57,110 --> 00:27:59,710
you shouldn't have trouble
finding a partner.

684
00:28:01,070 --> 00:28:02,570
If not for a blind date,

685
00:28:03,370 --> 00:28:05,170
why would you come out to meet me?

686
00:28:09,070 --> 00:28:10,930
Is that a hard question to answer?

687
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:12,560
No.

688
00:28:13,420 --> 00:28:14,440
It's just...

689
00:28:16,250 --> 00:28:17,990
this is my first blind date,

690
00:28:19,220 --> 00:28:21,750
and the person  I'm dating
is a police officer.

691
00:28:21,940 --> 00:28:23,270
I'm a little nervous.

692
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:28,050
Are you like this on all your blind dates?

693
00:28:28,570 --> 00:28:29,200
Like what?

694
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:30,770
Like...

695
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:34,550
like you're interrogating me.

696
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:38,210
I just don't think

697
00:28:38,210 --> 00:28:38,740
we're a good fit.

698
00:28:38,740 --> 00:28:40,400
We're not from the same world.

699
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,380
I believe

700
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,660
in first impressions.

701
00:28:47,540 --> 00:28:49,130
So, you're the type

702
00:28:49,320 --> 00:28:51,020
who makes snap judgments.

703
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:54,130
But you can't judge people

704
00:28:54,130 --> 00:28:55,400
only by their appearance.

705
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,180
After all...

706
00:28:56,760 --> 00:28:57,610
this is

707
00:28:57,660 --> 00:28:58,340
the first time we've met.

708
00:28:58,340 --> 00:28:58,940
This isn't

709
00:28:58,940 --> 00:29:00,110
the first time.

710
00:29:05,050 --> 00:29:05,660
After all this,

711
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:06,080
you still haven't

712
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:07,340
answered my question.

713
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,050
Why did you agree to meet me?

714
00:29:10,830 --> 00:29:11,690
What about you?

715
00:29:12,430 --> 00:29:13,080
Why did you agree

716
00:29:13,080 --> 00:29:14,060
to have a meal with me?

717
00:29:14,060 --> 00:29:15,120
To deal with my mom.

718
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:15,770
Me too.

719
00:29:15,830 --> 00:29:16,460
You're lying.

720
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:17,460
Do you have proof?

721
00:29:23,040 --> 00:29:23,700
Intuition.

722
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:29,880
If I were really a bad guy,

723
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:32,610
you wouldn't be able
to catch me like this.

724
00:29:33,430 --> 00:29:34,740
You and Bai Chun

725
00:29:34,770 --> 00:29:35,830
are nothing alike.

726
00:29:36,320 --> 00:29:37,570
He is an honest man.

727
00:29:38,300 --> 00:29:38,850
Back then—

728
00:29:38,850 --> 00:29:39,940
He is very capable.

729
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:42,420
How else could he
have become the mine chief?

730
00:29:44,560 --> 00:29:45,400
Our company's

731
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:46,700
Vice President Wu Jiang

732
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:47,890
outranks Bai Chun,

733
00:29:48,430 --> 00:29:50,360
but he's stuck managing Mine No. 2.

734
00:29:50,560 --> 00:29:52,690
So, he's always giving him a hard time.

735
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:54,120
I called him out on it a few times,

736
00:29:54,120 --> 00:29:55,860
and now he holds a grudge against me, too.

737
00:29:55,860 --> 00:29:57,630
The one who filed
that false report last time

738
00:29:57,630 --> 00:29:58,890
was probably Wu Jiang.

739
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,180
My job is to maintain order

740
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:03,250
and fight crime,

741
00:30:03,950 --> 00:30:04,960
not to help you and Chun

742
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:06,460
get rid of your competition.

743
00:30:06,460 --> 00:30:07,520
It's not like that.

744
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:09,600
I was just complaining to you

745
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:11,400
about my unreliable colleague.

746
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:13,440
I didn't intend to go after him.

747
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:15,140
But...

748
00:30:15,930 --> 00:30:16,740
Does Bai Chun

749
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:17,830
never talk to you

750
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:18,880
about his work?

751
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:20,330
Or do you

752
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:22,370
just not care?

753
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,970
Tianduo isn't that big,

754
00:30:25,600 --> 00:30:27,900
and the Xinhai mining area
isn't far at all.

755
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:28,620
We siblings

756
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:29,500
are very close.

757
00:30:30,410 --> 00:30:31,220
Then how come

758
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,500
you only know me today?

759
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:43,120
Han.

760
00:30:44,030 --> 00:30:45,170
I heard that a few days ago,

761
00:30:45,170 --> 00:30:46,570
you were caught by Bai Ju.

762
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,460
You stay here all day,

763
00:30:47,460 --> 00:30:48,990
but you're well-informed.

764
00:30:50,520 --> 00:30:52,180
Whatever happens in the city,

765
00:30:54,130 --> 00:30:55,400
the wind blowing from there

766
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:56,430
will tell me.

767
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,420
News about you has spread.

768
00:30:59,020 --> 00:31:00,140
Even the eagles on the snow mountains

769
00:31:00,140 --> 00:31:01,030
and the marmots on the ground

770
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:01,860
know about it.

771
00:31:04,210 --> 00:31:05,210
You talk too much.

772
00:31:05,550 --> 00:31:06,870
If you're so capable,
don't borrow money from me

773
00:31:06,870 --> 00:31:08,330
after the fine is settled.

774
00:31:08,370 --> 00:31:09,770
I'm borrowing it anyway.

775
00:31:09,990 --> 00:31:10,810
You seized

776
00:31:10,830 --> 00:31:12,160
so many pelts this time.

777
00:31:14,040 --> 00:31:15,100
A couple of days ago,

778
00:31:15,100 --> 00:31:16,560
County Mayor Lin came by.

779
00:31:16,940 --> 00:31:18,070
I think there's hope

780
00:31:18,080 --> 00:31:20,010
for your permanent positions.

781
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:21,640
Zhacuo.

782
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,180
County Mayor Lin

783
00:31:22,180 --> 00:31:23,240
is a Vice Mayor now, right?

784
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:24,130
Look at you, such a big shot.

785
00:31:24,130 --> 00:31:26,130
What brings him all the way out here?

786
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:27,880
It's been so many years.

787
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,780
When you hear "permanent position",

788
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:31,380
you act like a dog with a bone.

789
00:31:31,870 --> 00:31:33,310
Pay me back. Pay me back now.

790
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:34,750
I don't have any. I don't have any.

791
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:36,320
That's just Dad's nonsense.

792
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:36,950
To him,

793
00:31:36,980 --> 00:31:38,110
if you wear a jacket

794
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:38,960
and carry a briefcase,

795
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:40,360
you're County Mayor Lin.

796
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:42,560
It was Shao who came by a few days ago.

797
00:31:43,030 --> 00:31:45,290
He got snapped at by Bai again, didn't he?

798
00:31:45,670 --> 00:31:46,950
Shao told me

799
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:48,650
there's a problem with this pasture.

800
00:31:48,650 --> 00:31:49,330
Look.

801
00:31:49,860 --> 00:31:51,590
County Mayor Lin is here again.

802
00:32:00,590 --> 00:32:01,790
County Mayor Lin!

803
00:32:02,660 --> 00:32:03,530
Tashi Delek.

804
00:32:03,820 --> 00:32:04,710
Hello.

805
00:32:04,810 --> 00:32:06,180
Tashi Delek, sir.

806
00:32:08,010 --> 00:32:08,860
Mr. Zhacuo.

807
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:10,600
Hello, everyone.

808
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:12,290
I'm Meng Yaohui,

809
00:32:12,310 --> 00:32:13,120
General Manager

810
00:32:13,120 --> 00:32:14,050
of Xinhai Group.

811
00:32:15,230 --> 00:32:16,560
What are you doing here?

812
00:32:17,190 --> 00:32:18,790
I've heard of Xinhai. Hello.

813
00:32:19,490 --> 00:32:20,430
That's good.

814
00:32:21,020 --> 00:32:22,240
If you know us,

815
00:32:22,280 --> 00:32:23,110
then communicating

816
00:32:23,110 --> 00:32:24,240
will be much easier.

817
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:26,090
Xinhai Group

818
00:32:26,110 --> 00:32:26,920
is currently consolidating

819
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,260
the coal mines

820
00:32:28,770 --> 00:32:30,130
and handling some legacy issues

821
00:32:30,130 --> 00:32:30,850
regarding pasture acquisition

822
00:32:30,850 --> 00:32:32,060
and usage rights.

823
00:32:32,570 --> 00:32:33,180
I'm here

824
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:34,430
to talk about

825
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:36,320
the ownership of this grassland.

826
00:32:37,090 --> 00:32:38,290
This is the previous contract.

827
00:32:38,290 --> 00:32:38,950
Take a look.

828
00:32:39,010 --> 00:32:40,010
Here, Mr. Zhacuo.

829
00:32:47,210 --> 00:32:48,610
Look, what this is about.

830
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:54,900
Zhacuo.

831
00:32:56,220 --> 00:32:57,060
Did Ms. Cairen

832
00:32:57,090 --> 00:32:57,840
ever transfer

833
00:32:57,840 --> 00:32:59,170
this pasture back then?

834
00:33:00,180 --> 00:33:01,400
No, I don't think so.

835
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:03,060
Otherwise,

836
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:04,120
she wouldn't let me

837
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:04,830
graze here.

838
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:06,530
Then, where did

839
00:33:06,530 --> 00:33:07,930
this contract come from?

840
00:33:09,980 --> 00:33:10,480
I

841
00:33:10,620 --> 00:33:11,270
don't know.

842
00:33:11,270 --> 00:33:12,070
This contract

843
00:33:12,100 --> 00:33:12,680
was signed by Cairen

844
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:14,080
with Chenlong Coal Mine.

845
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:14,810
At the time, Cairen

846
00:33:14,810 --> 00:33:16,210
probably took a deposit.

847
00:33:16,390 --> 00:33:17,260
But Chenlong Coal Mine

848
00:33:17,260 --> 00:33:18,530
did not use this pasture

849
00:33:18,530 --> 00:33:19,360
within

850
00:33:19,390 --> 00:33:20,720
the stipulated validity period.

851
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,520
Now Chenlong has been merged into Xinhai.

852
00:33:22,520 --> 00:33:23,820
Xinhai wants to re-evaluate

853
00:33:23,820 --> 00:33:24,810
and purchase this pasture's

854
00:33:24,810 --> 00:33:25,260
usage rights.

855
00:33:25,260 --> 00:33:26,070
No need.

856
00:33:26,910 --> 00:33:28,320
We're not selling for any price.

857
00:33:28,320 --> 00:33:29,390
At current land prices,

858
00:33:29,390 --> 00:33:30,240
we definitely won't

859
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,650
let Miss Cairen lose out.

860
00:33:31,930 --> 00:33:32,550
After all,

861
00:33:32,580 --> 00:33:33,220
we are all

862
00:33:33,250 --> 00:33:34,400
from Mazhi County.

863
00:33:34,420 --> 00:33:34,910
You all know

864
00:33:34,910 --> 00:33:36,020
the friendship between our family

865
00:33:36,020 --> 00:33:37,110
and Duojie's family.

866
00:33:37,110 --> 00:33:38,150
You can rest assured.

867
00:33:38,150 --> 00:33:39,010
That's exactly

868
00:33:39,030 --> 00:33:40,090
why we're worried.

869
00:33:41,010 --> 00:33:41,600
Bai Chun.

870
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:42,810
You've got nothing

871
00:33:42,810 --> 00:33:44,120
but dollar signs in your eyes.

872
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:45,520
How dare you mention Duojie?

873
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:45,980
Han.

874
00:33:46,850 --> 00:33:48,350
Calm down first.

875
00:33:49,350 --> 00:33:50,770
It's not your pasture,

876
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,280
so you have no say in this.

877
00:33:52,700 --> 00:33:53,430
We're here

878
00:33:53,450 --> 00:33:54,040
to ask you

879
00:33:54,070 --> 00:33:55,140
to contact Cairen.

880
00:33:55,630 --> 00:33:56,790
Regarding this pasture,

881
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:58,180
we'll pay to use it

882
00:33:58,250 --> 00:33:59,730
and restore it afterwards.

883
00:33:59,730 --> 00:34:00,930
Restore?

884
00:34:01,850 --> 00:34:02,550
You think we can't see

885
00:34:02,550 --> 00:34:03,020
how high the cinder

886
00:34:03,020 --> 00:34:03,700
is piled?

887
00:34:04,150 --> 00:34:05,160
Do you take us for fools?

888
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:05,720
Han.

889
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:08,080
Duojie has been

890
00:34:08,489 --> 00:34:09,949
missing for so many years.

891
00:34:10,540 --> 00:34:12,070
And the contract is signed.

892
00:34:12,210 --> 00:34:13,060
What's the point

893
00:34:13,060 --> 00:34:14,500
of you clinging

894
00:34:15,210 --> 00:34:16,139
to this pasture?

895
00:34:17,130 --> 00:34:18,300
Does his disappearance
have to do with you?

896
00:34:18,300 --> 00:34:18,550
Han.

897
00:34:18,550 --> 00:34:19,150
Calm down.

898
00:34:19,199 --> 00:34:20,000
What business is it of yours?

899
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:20,310
Han.

900
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:21,090
Han.

901
00:34:21,110 --> 00:34:21,650
Get off the pasture!

902
00:34:21,650 --> 00:34:22,190
Han, calm down.

903
00:34:22,190 --> 00:34:22,590
Get out!

904
00:34:22,590 --> 00:34:22,940
Han.

905
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:23,440
Get out!

906
00:34:24,030 --> 00:34:24,420
Get out!

907
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:24,730
Han.

908
00:34:24,750 --> 00:34:25,310
Get out!

909
00:34:25,489 --> 00:34:26,949
Hit this County Mayor Lin!

910
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:28,020
Hit him! Hit him!

911
00:34:28,020 --> 00:34:28,630
Get the hell out!

912
00:34:28,630 --> 00:34:28,900
Han.

913
00:34:28,980 --> 00:34:29,780
What are you doing?

914
00:34:29,780 --> 00:34:30,510
Don't fight.

915
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:31,590
Stop.

916
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:33,110
You want to fight?

917
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:34,070
Don't fight.

918
00:34:40,380 --> 00:34:41,290
What are you doing?

919
00:34:41,290 --> 00:34:41,960
Let go!

920
00:34:55,659 --> 00:34:56,510
Just speak.

921
00:34:56,540 --> 00:34:57,560
Stop drinking.

922
00:34:58,220 --> 00:34:59,240
You called her.

923
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,100
I have nothing to say.

924
00:35:01,710 --> 00:35:02,750
You two remaining in this deadlock

925
00:35:02,750 --> 00:35:03,410
is not good.

926
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:04,600
Have a good talk.

927
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:06,550
Mind your own business.

928
00:35:08,380 --> 00:35:08,950
Why don't you go

929
00:35:08,950 --> 00:35:10,150
get Shao Yunfei here?

930
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:12,780
It's all because of
his nonsense reporting

931
00:35:12,780 --> 00:35:14,730
about promoting coal mine consolidation.

932
00:35:14,730 --> 00:35:15,900
With all of this,

933
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:17,960
Captain's pasture is about

934
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:19,220
to be in others' hands.

935
00:35:20,530 --> 00:35:22,010
Every debt has its debtor.

936
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:24,240
You can't

937
00:35:24,260 --> 00:35:25,900
blame Shao Yunfei.

938
00:35:26,500 --> 00:35:27,460
Besides,

939
00:35:27,580 --> 00:35:29,640
he's getting a headache over it, too.

940
00:35:29,950 --> 00:35:30,410
Right.

941
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:34,800
If you want to blame someone,
blame the coal mines,

942
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,610
blame Xinhai,

943
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:40,100
and blame some people

944
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:41,700
for not having a firm stance.

945
00:35:49,290 --> 00:35:50,340
I know all these years,

946
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:52,070
you haven't been able to let go.

947
00:35:52,210 --> 00:35:53,320
But not everyone

948
00:35:53,340 --> 00:35:54,530
has to be like you,

949
00:35:55,050 --> 00:35:56,030
going on a wild goose chase

950
00:35:56,030 --> 00:35:57,000
with a detector

951
00:35:57,030 --> 00:35:58,760
just to do right by the Captain.

952
00:35:59,230 --> 00:36:01,090
You have the nerve to mention him?

953
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:02,110
If you can,

954
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:03,430
why can't I?

955
00:36:03,520 --> 00:36:05,120
Bai, he drank his brains out.

956
00:36:05,250 --> 00:36:07,180
Don't lower yourself to his level.

957
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:16,100
It's been 17 years.

958
00:36:18,190 --> 00:36:19,210
In these 17 years,

959
00:36:20,140 --> 00:36:20,920
I went to prison

960
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:23,220
and questioned the convicts
from back then.

961
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:24,770
The Bureau also caught

962
00:36:24,790 --> 00:36:25,960
two fugitives involved in

963
00:36:25,960 --> 00:36:27,360
the Qima'er Gold Mine case.

964
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:29,360
You all know about the public trial.

965
00:36:29,640 --> 00:36:30,750
But the information they provided

966
00:36:30,750 --> 00:36:31,670
had nothing to do

967
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:33,470
with Captain's disappearance.

968
00:36:33,870 --> 00:36:35,070
Li Yongqiang's funds

969
00:36:35,090 --> 00:36:36,090
came from abroad back then.

970
00:36:36,090 --> 00:36:38,150
We didn't have the jurisdiction
to trace them.

971
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:39,000
And his family

972
00:36:39,020 --> 00:36:39,820
left the country long ago.

973
00:36:39,820 --> 00:36:40,420
Since then,

974
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,880
they have never returned.

975
00:36:42,070 --> 00:36:42,800
The Public Security Bureau

976
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,290
has regularly

977
00:36:43,290 --> 00:36:44,400
informed Miss Cairen.

978
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:45,830
No one has forgotten him.

979
00:36:47,290 --> 00:36:49,350
Is it fair for you to say that about us?

980
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:54,270
I've said before,

981
00:36:54,610 --> 00:36:57,870
environmental protection
doesn't come from protesting.

982
00:36:58,340 --> 00:37:00,200
I believe even if Captain were here,

983
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:01,200
he wouldn't agree

984
00:37:01,210 --> 00:37:02,740
with what you're doing now.

985
00:37:09,740 --> 00:37:10,350
Do you know

986
00:37:10,380 --> 00:37:12,310
why the city wants to open the mine?

987
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:16,070
For the coal bosses to make money.

988
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:16,590
Yes.

989
00:37:16,800 --> 00:37:18,460
The coal bosses do make money.

990
00:37:18,560 --> 00:37:19,420
But a large part

991
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,360
of the tax revenue

992
00:37:20,360 --> 00:37:21,760
relies on the coal mines.

993
00:37:21,770 --> 00:37:23,150
Don't think just because Chun
is the mine chief,

994
00:37:23,150 --> 00:37:24,930
our family is benefiting from them.

995
00:37:24,930 --> 00:37:26,010
To put it bluntly,

996
00:37:26,680 --> 00:37:27,930
everyone here,

997
00:37:28,060 --> 00:37:29,220
every citizen of Tianduo,

998
00:37:29,220 --> 00:37:30,720
is benefiting from them.

999
00:37:31,750 --> 00:37:33,010
Take you, Han Xuechao.

1000
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:35,300
You work as a security guard at the mall.

1001
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:36,300
If there were no coal mines,

1002
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:36,890
the economy

1003
00:37:36,890 --> 00:37:37,690
wouldn't be this good.

1004
00:37:37,690 --> 00:37:38,960
There wouldn't be a mall,

1005
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,960
and you'd have no mall gate to watch!

1006
00:37:41,110 --> 00:37:42,170
Alright, alright.

1007
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:43,880
The priority now

1008
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:44,640
is to talk to Miss Cairen

1009
00:37:44,640 --> 00:37:45,700
about the pasture.

1010
00:37:47,280 --> 00:37:48,000
Mr. Meng

1011
00:37:48,020 --> 00:37:49,540
said one thing right.

1012
00:37:50,410 --> 00:37:51,810
This pasture isn't ours.

1013
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:53,850
We don't have a say in it.

1014
00:37:59,010 --> 00:37:59,950
Tashi said

1015
00:38:00,670 --> 00:38:02,200
his mom is in poor health now

1016
00:38:02,250 --> 00:38:03,860
and doesn't want to come back.

1017
00:38:03,860 --> 00:38:05,420
She's afraid that if she comes back,

1018
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:06,750
she'll think of Captain

1019
00:38:07,620 --> 00:38:08,750
and be heartbroken.

1020
00:38:10,300 --> 00:38:10,900
Tashi wants

1021
00:38:10,900 --> 00:38:12,400
to keep this pasture.

1022
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:13,650
Actually,

1023
00:38:14,390 --> 00:38:15,770
if we really get into it,

1024
00:38:16,290 --> 00:38:18,150
we might not have a leg to stand on.

1025
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:20,920
And Xinhai is such a big enterprise.

1026
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:22,130
If they're dead set

1027
00:38:22,130 --> 00:38:23,300
on getting this land,

1028
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:25,100
they have plenty of ways to do it.

1029
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:26,790
What kind of means?

1030
00:38:27,410 --> 00:38:29,350
This is a society governed by law.

1031
00:38:29,700 --> 00:38:30,430
Fine.

1032
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:32,140
If Xinhai files a lawsuit,

1033
00:38:32,370 --> 00:38:33,360
can we win?

1034
00:38:33,890 --> 00:38:35,270
Even if we could,

1035
00:38:35,350 --> 00:38:36,480
lawyers cost money,

1036
00:38:37,100 --> 00:38:38,700
and litigation costs money.

1037
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:43,900
I think

1038
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:45,530
we should just transfer it.

1039
00:38:45,870 --> 00:38:46,620
Xinhai said

1040
00:38:46,650 --> 00:38:48,110
they'd offer a good price.

1041
00:38:48,690 --> 00:38:50,110
Is this about money?

1042
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,870
If Captain were here,

1043
00:38:55,050 --> 00:38:55,820
he would never

1044
00:38:55,820 --> 00:38:56,970
let any pasture

1045
00:38:56,990 --> 00:38:58,320
be covered in coal slag!

1046
00:39:00,510 --> 00:39:01,200
Han.

1047
00:39:02,230 --> 00:39:03,710
Are you criticizing me?

1048
00:39:07,670 --> 00:39:08,670
No.

1049
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:12,500
No.

1050
00:39:15,380 --> 00:39:17,190
If we really sell the pasture,

1051
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:22,540
what if Captain's soul comes back

1052
00:39:24,190 --> 00:39:25,720
and can't find his way home?

1053
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:27,950
What do you mean by that, Han?

1054
00:39:28,700 --> 00:39:29,630
Ask the Tibetans

1055
00:39:29,650 --> 00:39:30,850
if they believe that.

1056
00:39:31,370 --> 00:39:31,880
Besides,

1057
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:33,410
is it your place to say that?

1058
00:39:34,270 --> 00:39:35,190
He has been missing

1059
00:39:35,190 --> 00:39:35,960
for 17 years.

1060
00:39:36,410 --> 00:39:37,010
Ms. Cairen

1061
00:39:37,010 --> 00:39:38,380
and Tashi don't live here.

1062
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:39,590
Why keep this land?

1063
00:39:39,690 --> 00:39:40,390
Sangba.

1064
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:01,190
Han.

1065
00:40:06,720 --> 00:40:07,700
I'm

1066
00:40:09,260 --> 00:40:10,790
on the night shift tonight.

1067
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,390
I'll see him out.

1068
00:40:34,710 --> 00:40:35,330
Bai Ju.

1069
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:37,830
Take this.

1070
00:40:39,470 --> 00:40:40,930
It's homemade yak jerky.

1071
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,640
For Lingling.

1072
00:40:44,270 --> 00:40:45,320
Kids need nutrition

1073
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:46,260
when they're growing.

1074
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:46,760
Thanks.

1075
00:40:46,860 --> 00:40:47,860
Don't mention it.

1076
00:40:50,700 --> 00:40:51,640
Han...

1077
00:40:52,210 --> 00:40:52,980
You know him.

1078
00:40:56,430 --> 00:40:57,170
All these years,

1079
00:40:57,170 --> 00:40:58,210
he's been alone.

1080
00:40:59,530 --> 00:41:00,230
Regarding Captain,

1081
00:41:00,230 --> 00:41:01,490
he took it the hardest.

1082
00:41:02,110 --> 00:41:03,280
Sometimes I think

1083
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:06,960
having this hope to hold onto

1084
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:08,170
is a good thing.

1085
00:41:09,370 --> 00:41:10,230
Otherwise, I don't know

1086
00:41:10,230 --> 00:41:10,860
how he would have survived

1087
00:41:10,860 --> 00:41:11,950
all these years.

1088
00:41:13,030 --> 00:41:14,010
Do you think

1089
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:16,560
I blame him?

1090
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:19,500
I'm saying you're different.

1091
00:41:19,750 --> 00:41:20,770
You have a family.

1092
00:41:23,680 --> 00:41:26,480
You don't need to pass on
messages for Shao Yunfei.

1093
00:41:26,980 --> 00:41:28,910
This is what I want to tell you, too.

1094
00:41:29,810 --> 00:41:31,010
To investigate this,

1095
00:41:32,100 --> 00:41:34,430
you haven't had
any other baby for 7 years.

1096
00:41:35,120 --> 00:41:36,380
You've done enough,

1097
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:37,050
Bai.

1098
00:41:43,370 --> 00:41:44,300
Have you

1099
00:41:45,770 --> 00:41:48,170
dreamed of the Mountain Patrol after that?

1100
00:41:49,890 --> 00:41:50,530
Of course.

1101
00:41:53,060 --> 00:41:54,520
Do you dream of them often?

1102
00:41:57,780 --> 00:41:58,510
Bai.

1103
00:42:00,410 --> 00:42:02,070
Streams thin out as they flow.

1104
00:42:03,380 --> 00:42:05,040
Grass grows coarse as it ages.

1105
00:42:05,660 --> 00:42:06,990
Things fade over time.

1106
00:42:07,020 --> 00:42:08,280
Everything will pass.

1107
00:42:16,510 --> 00:42:17,200
Yes.

1108
00:42:19,330 --> 00:42:20,390
He used to say,

1109
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:23,860
"Everyone leaves eventually."

1110
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,720
After we're gone,

1111
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:30,350
no one will

1112
00:42:30,370 --> 00:42:31,480
dream of Bolamula.

1113
00:42:34,600 --> 00:42:36,040
And no one will remember

1114
00:42:38,090 --> 00:42:39,620
that this was once his home.

1115
00:42:44,970 --> 00:42:46,510
I hope I can guard this place

1116
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:50,570
and keep it

1117
00:42:50,590 --> 00:42:51,570
the way it was.

1118
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:54,940
Sometimes,

1119
00:42:55,110 --> 00:42:56,570
the things people forget,

1120
00:42:57,980 --> 00:42:59,510
the land remembers for you.

1121
00:43:06,120 --> 00:43:09,790
[Bolamula: Ordinary Lives
on the Anti-Poaching Front Lines]
